data.description: Possibilities are endless in this charming rustic home! Situated on almost 15 acres, this home features a new roof in September 2022. Newly built Pole Barn, perfect for storing tractors and equipment, cross fencing surrounding entire property, triple road frontage and accessibility, creek access, established fruit trees and vines, and chicken coop. Bring your cows, goats, chickens and kids and see what all this home has to offer!! Sellers are motivated!
